    <item>
      <title>WeWork 债权人要求公司与潜在买家进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/wework-creditors-demand-company-negotiate-with-potential-buyers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个由低级别债权人组成的小组在 2019 年 11 月表示，联合办公巨头 WeWork Inc. 应该被迫与潜在买家（可能包括联合创始人 Adam Neumann）进行谈判，并在 30 天的期限内提出退出破产的计划。法庭文件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/wework-creditors-demand-company-negotiate-with-potential-buyers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 15:35:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于石化和税收支出疲弱，Reliance 未达到利润预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/ambani-s-reliance-misses-profit-estimate-on-petrochemicals-drag</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁穆克什·安巴尼(Mukesh Ambani)领导的信实工业有限公司(Reliance Industries Ltd.)公布的季度利润低于预期，原因是石化业务持续疲软，税收增加抵消了消费部门的增长和其他收入的大幅增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/ambani-s-reliance-misses-profit-estimate-on-petrochemicals-drag</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 13:40:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
